     Description:
         Color token definitions for the Catppuccin Mocha theme. Soft pastel dark
         palette (#1E1E2E base, #CBA6F7 Mauve accent, #CDD6F4 text).
         The most trendy dark theme of 2024-2026.

     Architecture Notes:
         ResourceDictionary. Consumed as the first merged dictionary in CatppuccinMochaTheme.xaml.
         Defines all Dock* and Panel_* keys required by Dark/ shared templates
         and PanelCommon.xaml.
     ========================================================== -->

